\begin_layout Standard
We have considered a model where status amounts to a position that only
 temporarily cements the participant's economic position.
 With a decision theory framework for uncertainty, the goal of the model
 has been to investigate role of income difference on expenditures that
 carry some status while also having some effect on the income mobility
 of the participants.
